data.lettercontent: Hello. I am a fan from Shaanxi, China. I know you must know China, but Shaanxi may not be known to you, but it doesn't matter. Just remember that I am your Chinese fan and there are many people who love you in China. Although you may not see this letter, I still want to write to you. From the first time I saw you to now, I thought you were a very cold person from the beginning, but now I think you are cute and responsible. It didn't take a long time, I don't know why, but I have always vaguely felt that you are a very easy to get along with. After getting to know you, sometimes I will see your responsible side, and sometimes I will see you and your members acting coquettishly. The ever-changing nature of you makes me feel that you are a person worth being loved, I hope you and your members can be healthy and happy every day in the future. Please remember me, I will always be behind you. As long as you turn your head, you can see me. Don't worry about me walking away. I will always be there and support you. Fighting!
